---
description: JSON Schema and component protocol editing rules
globs: ["frontend/src/schema/**"]
alwaysApply: false
---

Before editing these files, read:
- `AGENTS.md`
- `.ai/instructions/schema-protocol.md`

Rules:
- Every component protocol must include `aiHints` array.
- Protocol `type` must match `ComponentType` union value exactly.
- Register new protocols in `protocols/index.ts` componentProtocols map.
- `componentProtocol.ts` is a compatibility re-export layer — add new code in `./protocols/`.
